on the murder suspects,

275
00:17:48,465 --> 00:17:49,826
Zhuo Bufan and Yu Huanjie.

276
00:17:55,666 --> 00:17:56,192
Master.

277
00:17:56,512 --> 00:17:57,344
Sorry to disturb you.

278
00:17:58,272 --> 00:17:59,455
(Constable of Dagu County Yamen)
I'm Wang Jialuo,

279
00:17:59,455 --> 00:18:00,426
a constable of Dagu County Yamen.

280
00:18:00,426 --> 00:18:03,146
I came all the way to catch
Zhuo Bufan and Yu Huanjie,

281
00:18:03,346 --> 00:18:04,992
murderers of Dagu Murder Case
of Nine Deaths.

282
00:18:05,426 --> 00:18:07,545
Also, I'm investigating the case

283
00:18:07,785 --> 00:18:08,586
of the Altar Treasure

284
00:18:09,426 --> 00:18:12,025
to prevent the national treasure
from being stolen by others,

285
00:18:12,505 --> 00:18:13,265
endangering the court.

286
00:18:15,186 --> 00:18:17,186
When did the constable's uniform change?

287
00:18:20,586 --> 00:18:21,888
This is the uniform of Beiyang Army.

288
00:18:22,225 --> 00:18:24,066
Coincidentally,

289
00:18:24,066 --> 00:18:25,866
I became a second lieutenant
of the 43rd Association.

290
00:18:26,386 --> 00:18:27,305
Whether a constable

291
00:18:27,305 --> 00:18:27,945
or Beiyang soldier,

292
00:18:27,945 --> 00:18:28,985
both serve the court

293
00:18:28,985 --> 00:18:30,705
and should abide by the laws.

294
00:18:34,025 --> 00:18:34,626
Master.

295
00:18:35,626 --> 00:18:37,545
I guess

296
00:18:37,985 --> 00:18:39,386
you stopped them.

297
00:18:42,066 --> 00:18:43,745
But I need to enter for a fair search.

298
00:18:45,426 --> 00:18:46,146
Please do not

299
00:18:46,985 --> 00:18:47,626
stop me.

300
00:18:50,066 --> 00:18:50,985
Whoever crosses the line

301
00:18:51,985 --> 00:18:52,745
will be taken down.

302
00:19:10,025 --> 00:19:11,025
I know you're serious.

303
00:19:11,666 --> 00:19:13,505
Zhuo Bufan's martial arts
are unparalleled,

304
00:19:13,505 --> 00:19:14,225
but he failed.

305
00:19:15,106 --> 00:19:16,305
Naturally, I am no match for you.

306
00:19:17,106 --> 00:19:17,664
However,

307
00:19:19,346 --> 00:19:19,906
I have a gun.

308
00:19:24,146 --> 00:19:25,866
I don't believe any martial skill

309
00:19:25,866 --> 00:19:27,025
can exceed the speed of a bullet.

310
00:19:27,785 --> 00:19:28,785
Jialuo, you don't need to act.

311
00:19:29,305 --> 00:19:30,025
Let them do it.

312
00:19:32,666 --> 00:19:34,225
You guys go ahead.

313
00:19:36,346 --> 00:19:37,472
If he dares to make a move,

314
00:19:38,586 --> 00:19:39,186
shoot him.

315
00:19:53,305 --> 00:19:54,426
I'll shoot you.

316
00:20:02,745 --> 00:20:03,328
Don't move.

317
00:20:04,545 --> 00:20:05,344
Put the gun down.

318
00:20:16,866 --> 00:20:17,545
Put the gun down!

319
00:20:23,666 --> 00:20:24,426
Master.

320
00:20:24,545 --> 00:20:25,866
Sorry for offense.

321
00:20:25,866 --> 00:20:26,826
Please do not hurt him.

322
00:20:27,265 --> 00:20:28,186
Whoever crosses the line

323
00:20:28,545 --> 00:20:29,505
will be taken down.

324
00:20:29,505 --> 00:20:30,146
Master.

325
00:20:30,146 --> 00:20:32,146
It's important.
I must go in for the investigation.

326
00:20:33,025 --> 00:20:33,785
Go ahead.

327
00:20:36,945 --> 00:20:37,545
Jialuo.

328
00:20:39,106 --> 00:20:40,186
He is no ordinary person.

329
00:20:45,066 --> 00:20:46,225
Zhuo Bufan has run away again.

330
00:20:47,146 --> 00:20:47,985
Guys, chase him!

331
00:20:59,225 --> 00:21:02,505
Even if the Altar Treasure is real,
neither you nor I can get it.

332
00:21:04,705 --> 00:21:06,945
The treasure map on the banned book
shelf of Wenyuan Pavilion

333
00:21:06,945 --> 00:21:08,265
has long been stolen.

334
00:21:08,386 --> 00:21:09,826
That's why I was released

335
00:21:10,186 --> 00:21:12,785
to investigate the case
after being imprisoned for 12 years.

336
00:21:13,025 --> 00:21:14,186
It was stolen?

337
00:21:14,186 --> 00:21:15,106
Zhuo Bufan

338
00:21:15,106 --> 00:21:16,545
has the Discipline Seal.

339
00:21:17,025 --> 00:21:19,346
If the Discipline Seal
in the Wenyuan Pavilion

340
00:21:19,346 --> 00:21:20,146
hadn't been stolen,

341
00:21:20,146 --> 00:21:22,305
you wouldn't have had the chance
to be released.

342
00:21:23,106 --> 00:21:25,346
If you didn't come all the way here,

343
00:21:25,386 --> 00:21:26,465
you wouldn't know

344
00:21:26,626 --> 00:21:28,066
that you are
Bodhi Department's inheritor.

345
00:21:29,106 --> 00:21:30,705
It is the entangled causes and effects

346
00:21:31,186 --> 00:21:32,705
that have led to today's meeting.

347
00:21:33,985 --> 00:21:35,025
The cause is the start.

348
00:21:35,586 --> 00:21:36,465
The effect is the result.

349
00:21:36,945 --> 00:21:38,066
The cause and effect

350
00:21:38,745 --> 00:21:39,705
are far from certain.

351
00:21:41,025 --> 00:21:41,745
Alright.

352
00:21:41,745 --> 00:21:43,225
I have said what I should say.

353
00:21:43,906 --> 00:21:46,586
You can't stay in the Futu Temple.

354
00:21:46,906 --> 00:21:48,745
Where should I go?

355
00:21:49,426 --> 00:21:50,265
You're a detective.

356
00:21:51,826 --> 00:21:52,505
But I am not.

357
00:21:57,225 --> 00:21:58,066
Thank you.

358
00:22:01,906 --> 00:22:02,826
Just now you said

359
00:22:02,826 --> 00:22:04,866
you were glad I did not make a move.

360
00:22:04,866 --> 00:22:07,505
Otherwise, the Bodhi Department
would have no inheritor.

361
00:22:09,106 --> 00:22:11,826
I wonder if you're trying to scare me

362
00:22:12,106 --> 00:22:13,426
or if you can defeat me.

363
00:22:18,985 --> 00:22:20,505
I never lie.

364
00:22:36,666 --> 00:22:37,426
You refuse to give in.

365
00:22:38,066 --> 00:22:38,666
That's very good.

366
00:22:39,626 --> 00:22:40,265
One should not

367
00:22:40,745 --> 00:22:41,985
admit defeat.

368
00:22:44,586 --> 00:22:45,426
What kung fu is this?

369
00:22:47,146 --> 00:22:49,666
Dragon-Subduing Skill
of Southern Shaolin.

370
00:22:51,586 --> 00:22:52,225
Thanks.

371
00:22:53,705 --> 00:22:55,265
If my rival is Cheng Yu,

372
00:22:55,545 --> 00:22:56,745
I will be defeated.

373
00:22:57,586 --> 00:22:59,745
You have obtained the Sanyin Sword.

374
00:23:00,505 --> 00:23:01,225
Practice it well.

375
00:23:02,186 --> 00:23:03,386
Do not let the Bodhi Department

376
00:23:03,626 --> 00:23:04,346
lose its legacy.

377
00:23:06,465 --> 00:23:07,666
My master passed away here.

378
00:23:08,305 --> 00:23:09,426
Where is his spiritual tablet?

379
00:23:09,586 --> 00:23:10,785
I want to pay my respects.

380
00:23:25,705 --> 00:23:26,745
You found the Altar Treasure?

381
00:23:27,626 --> 00:23:28,785
It's not that easy.

382
00:23:31,866 --> 00:23:32,586
Our people.

383
00:23:33,225 --> 00:23:34,848
They're pursuing the people
from Rongtian Ridge.

384
00:23:34,985 --> 00:23:35,826
Zhuo Bufan must be alive.

385
00:23:44,906 --> 00:23:45,426
How is it?

386
00:23:50,146 --> 00:23:51,465
Zhuo Bufan and Yu Huanjie

387
00:23:51,465 --> 00:23:52,265
have escaped.

388
00:23:57,106 --> 00:23:58,346
Why we can't kill Zhuo Bufan?

389
00:24:13,386 --> 00:24:15,465
I found another treasure map

390
00:24:15,465 --> 00:24:17,626
in the Futu Temple.

391
00:24:19,265 --> 00:24:20,906
It's the Bodhi Seal.

392
00:24:21,705 --> 00:24:23,025
This is only half of the whole map.

393
00:24:24,146 --> 00:24:25,066
And the other half

394
00:24:25,066 --> 00:24:27,025
is the one that was stolen
from the palace.

395
00:24:27,106 --> 00:24:28,265
It's the Discipline Seal.

396
00:24:28,705 --> 00:24:30,186
Now Zhuo Bufan has it.

397
00:24:31,305 --> 00:24:32,465
To unlock the treasure,

398
00:24:32,505 --> 00:24:35,186
we must combine the two seals.

399
00:24:35,826 --> 00:24:37,826
If we fail to find the Discipline Seal

400
00:24:37,826 --> 00:24:39,426
before killing Zhuo Bufan,

401
00:24:39,866 --> 00:24:41,265
the hope of finding the treasure

402
00:24:41,386 --> 00:24:42,705
will become very slim.

403
00:24:45,186 --> 00:24:46,705
Finding the treasure is your job.

404
00:24:47,265 --> 00:24:48,666
My job is to pursue the murderers.

405
00:24:49,305 --> 00:24:50,426
Moreover, I think

406
00:24:50,426 --> 00:24:52,545
finding the treasure
is not that important.

407
00:24:52,866 --> 00:24:55,025
As long as Zhuo Bufan
doesn't get the treasure,

408
00:24:55,025 --> 00:24:56,586
eliminating the threat to the court

409
00:24:56,906 --> 00:24:57,545
is enough.

410
00:24:58,626 --> 00:25:00,066
Why are you so stubborn?

411
00:25:00,066 --> 00:25:01,945
Catching a minor bandit

412
00:25:01,945 --> 00:25:02,826
is no big deal.

413
00:25:03,066 --> 00:25:05,265
Finding treasure for the court
is of utmost importance.

414
00:25:05,265 --> 00:25:07,626
Catching Zhuo Bufan
exemplifies the strictness of the laws

415
00:25:07,626 --> 00:25:09,025
and the orderliness of practices.

416
00:25:09,025 --> 00:25:11,626
Being resolute
is what an official ought to do.

417
00:25:11,626 --> 00:25:13,505
You're a lowly constable.

418
00:25:13,626 --> 00:25:15,505
Can you call yourself an official?

419
00:25:16,025 --> 00:25:16,945
Given your insights,

420
00:25:16,945 --> 00:25:19,705
you're not worthy of the high position
bestowed by the Emperor.

421
00:25:19,705 --> 00:25:21,066
Enough, guys.

422
00:25:21,066 --> 00:25:22,186
No need to argue.

423
00:25:22,186 --> 00:25:23,426
We are on the same team.

424
00:25:23,705 --> 00:25:25,465
Why do I have to work
with this stubborn man?

425
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:30,745
By the way,

426
00:25:31,826 --> 00:25:32,945
how did you get in?

427
00:25:33,346 --> 00:25:34,346
What do you mean?

428
00:25:34,906 --> 00:25:35,785
Futu Temple.

429
00:25:38,066 --> 00:25:39,426
That monk is too powerful.

430
00:25:39,426 --> 00:25:40,866
Both Zhuo Bufan and I couldn't enter.

431
00:25:40,866 --> 00:25:41,826
How did you get in?

432
00:25:42,626 --> 00:25:43,945
At first, he didn't get in either.

433
00:25:44,066 --> 00:25:45,346
Later, a young monk came.

434
00:25:45,346 --> 00:25:46,106
He let him in.

435
00:25:46,705 --> 00:25:47,666
Young monk?

436
00:25:48,025 --> 00:25:48,544
Yeah.

437
00:25:49,186 --> 00:25:50,066
The abbot.

438
00:25:50,826 --> 00:25:51,785
I don't

439
00:25:53,106 --> 00:25:53,985
know why.

440
00:25:56,346 --> 00:25:57,386
Let me tell you.

441
00:25:58,265 --> 00:25:59,465
Liu Lin and I

442
00:25:59,465 --> 00:26:00,426
entered the temple.

443
00:26:01,066 --> 00:26:03,186
Liu Lin could enter
because she had the passphrase.

444
00:26:03,386 --> 00:26:05,106
Tan Xian, the guy who died in Shanghai,

445
00:26:05,106 --> 00:26:05,826
told her.

446
00:26:06,545 --> 00:26:08,225
The young monk told me the secrets

447
00:26:08,225 --> 00:26:09,305
of the Futu Temple.

448
00:26:09,945 --> 00:26:11,025
The inheritor we looked for

449
00:26:11,025 --> 00:26:12,586
in Shanxi is the third generation chief

450
00:26:13,146 --> 00:26:16,545
of the Bodhi Department
of Southern Shaolin.

451
00:26:17,225 --> 00:26:18,826
He passed away in Futu Temple.

452
00:26:22,386 --> 00:26:23,225
Did you get the seal?

453
00:26:23,826 --> 00:26:24,705
I got nothing.

454
00:26:26,586 --> 00:26:28,866
The Bodhi's inheritor
has destroyed the seal.

455
00:26:28,985 --> 00:26:30,626
Why not kill Zhuo Bufan?

456
00:26:30,626 --> 00:26:31,945
I have come this far

457
00:26:31,945 --> 00:26:33,106
and had more and more clues.

458
00:26:33,106 --> 00:26:34,666
I have to keep investigating.

459
00:26:35,465 --> 00:26:36,025
Alright.

460
00:26:36,545 --> 00:26:37,545
You'll look for clues.

461
00:26:37,945 --> 00:26:39,265
I'll look for the murderers.

462
00:26:40,346 --> 00:26:41,626
I warn you.

463
00:26:41,866 --> 00:26:43,545
I don't care about whom you arrest.

464
00:26:43,545 --> 00:26:45,586
But I must get the Discipline Seal

465
00:26:45,586 --> 00:26:46,426
from Zhuo Bufan.

466
00:26:47,945 --> 00:26:48,545
No problem.

467
00:26:49,985 --> 00:26:51,906
Whether I capture or kill him,

468
00:26:51,906 --> 00:26:52,785
as long as I see the item,

469
00:26:53,106 --> 00:26:53,856
I'll give it to you.

470
00:27:03,866 --> 00:27:05,146
Why did you get in?

471
00:27:08,666 --> 00:27:10,505
That woman had a passphrase.

472
00:27:10,505 --> 00:27:11,505
But you didn't.

473
00:27:11,505 --> 00:27:12,386
How did you get in?

474
00:27:16,305 --> 00:27:17,426
40 years ago, the guards

475
00:27:17,426 --> 00:27:20,106
from the Imperial Household Department
had investigated Futu Temple,

476
00:27:20,106 --> 00:27:20,985
but found nothing.

477
00:27:21,545 --> 00:27:22,906
The young monk let me in

478
00:27:22,906 --> 00:27:24,346
just to make me give up,

479
00:27:24,346 --> 00:27:26,346
because the secrets there are worthless.

480
00:27:37,386 --> 00:27:38,106
Muqing.

481
00:27:38,985 --> 00:27:40,945
Did you really find nothing?

482
00:27:56,626 --> 00:27:58,106
You indeed got it.

483
00:28:01,146 --> 00:28:01,985
Take a look.

484
00:28:02,305 --> 00:28:03,906
Whether I tell Wang Jialuo or not

485
00:28:03,906 --> 00:28:06,265
makes no difference.

486
00:28:11,465 --> 00:28:12,186
It's really gone.

487
00:28:12,826 --> 00:28:13,426
Yes.

488
00:28:14,906 --> 00:28:16,186
However, I think

489
00:28:16,545 --> 00:28:18,985
we're getting closer to the truth.

490
00:28:19,945 --> 00:28:21,346
So, what's the next step?

491
00:28:21,346 --> 00:28:22,112
Return to the capital.

492
00:28:22,426 --> 00:28:24,626
I want to sort out all the clues.

493
00:28:25,146 --> 00:28:25,984
What about Zhuo Bufan?

494
00:28:32,066 --> 00:28:33,586
Here is

495
00:28:33,586 --> 00:28:35,146
the most delightful thing.

496
00:28:35,545 --> 00:28:37,066
Zhuo Bufan will surely think

497
00:28:37,066 --> 00:28:38,985
I have the Bodhi Seal.

498
00:28:39,826 --> 00:28:41,386
He will definitely follow us.

499
00:28:41,386 --> 00:28:41,985
So,

500
00:28:42,586 --> 00:28:43,985
he has the Discipline Seal,

501
00:28:43,985 --> 00:28:44,945
which is very safe.

502
00:28:46,265 --> 00:28:47,146
What about Liu Lin?

503
00:28:48,106 --> 00:28:49,305
Take her to the Ministry of Justice?

504
00:28:50,025 --> 00:28:50,906
Keep her for now.

505
00:28:50,906 --> 00:28:52,305
I'm not sure if she knows

506
00:28:52,305 --> 00:28:53,225
other secrets.

507
00:28:53,626 --> 00:28:54,176
Okay.

508
00:28:55,305 --> 00:28:56,066
By the way, Getai,

509
00:28:56,906 --> 00:28:59,025
don't mention Liu Lin to others for now.

510
00:28:59,586 --> 00:29:01,666
After all, she's a rebel
from the Tongmenghui.

511
00:29:01,666 --> 00:29:03,785
I don't want to cause any trouble.

512
00:29:04,186 --> 00:29:05,785
Finding the treasure
is the priority right now.

513
00:29:06,505 --> 00:29:07,346
I understand.

514
00:29:33,025 --> 00:29:35,346
(The next move I make
is called the Swordfall.)

515
00:29:35,552 --> 00:29:36,066
(One sword...)

516
00:29:36,066 --> 00:29:36,985
(One sword with six moves.)

517
00:29:36,985 --> 00:29:38,386
(Each move
with seven variations, right?)

518
00:29:42,066 --> 00:29:43,346
Isn't it still just one sword?

519
00:29:59,305 --> 00:30:00,505
You've been sitting here for long.

520
00:30:08,386 --> 00:30:08,985
I know

521
00:30:09,426 --> 00:30:11,386
that old monk made you upset today.

522
00:30:13,225 --> 00:30:13,945
I'm not upset.

523
00:30:14,505 --> 00:30:15,545
I'm really not upset at all.

524
00:30:19,225 --> 00:30:19,808
Bufan.

525
00:30:20,545 --> 00:30:21,346
It's okay.

526
00:30:21,985 --> 00:30:24,066
There are few people
like him in the world.

527
00:30:25,386 --> 00:30:26,265
The world is too vast.

528
00:30:27,745 --> 00:30:29,985
Martial Uncle Mo Kun showed me
the Sanyin Sword.

529
00:30:30,906 --> 00:30:33,545
Du E let me witness the legacy
of the Southern Shaolin.

530
00:30:35,465 --> 00:30:37,225
He said when the sword
of Bodhi Department is drawn,

531
00:30:37,465 --> 00:30:38,586
no one can fight back.

532
00:30:39,146 --> 00:30:40,586
But our swordsmanship

533
00:30:41,186 --> 00:30:42,146
is overly complicated.

534
00:30:44,066 --> 00:30:44,906
I can understand

535
00:30:45,705 --> 00:30:46,465
what he said.

536
00:30:47,386 --> 00:30:48,225
And it makes sense to me.

537
00:30:48,866 --> 00:30:49,586
Bufan.

538
00:30:50,505 --> 00:30:52,146
I'm really not sad at all.

539
00:30:52,225 --> 00:30:54,225
I want to find the Altar Treasure
as soon as possible

540
00:30:54,866 --> 00:30:56,386
and get the martial arts manuals inside.

541
00:30:57,826 --> 00:30:59,626
I want to make Rongtian Swordsmanship

542
00:30:59,626 --> 00:31:00,545
different.

543
00:31:01,545 --> 00:31:02,985
When the Rongtian Sword is drawn,

544
00:31:03,586 --> 00:31:04,705
no one can fight back.

545
00:31:05,465 --> 00:31:06,386
You can do it.

546
00:31:06,785 --> 00:31:07,906
I trust you.

547
00:31:09,705 --> 00:31:10,305
Right.

548
00:31:10,906 --> 00:31:12,586
So, why should I be sad?

549
00:31:14,985 --> 00:31:16,225
This is the real you.

550
00:31:16,465 --> 00:31:17,906
This is Zhuo Bufan.

551
00:31:19,505 --> 00:31:21,346
You refuse to lose.

552
00:31:21,866 --> 00:31:23,225
You always win.

553
00:31:23,705 --> 00:31:25,545
Even when facing someone stronger,

554
00:31:25,545 --> 00:31:26,945
you will feel more excited.

555
00:31:28,705 --> 00:31:30,146
Back at the main altar,

556
00:31:30,705 --> 00:31:32,586
you wanted
to challenge a famous swordsman,

557
00:31:32,785 --> 00:31:34,545
As I saw you off,

558
00:31:34,545 --> 00:31:36,066
I said that you would win.

559
00:31:37,626 --> 00:31:38,465
You said something to me.

560
00:31:39,186 --> 00:31:41,025
A broad chest harbors soaring clouds.

561
00:31:41,025 --> 00:31:42,705
Determined eyes track the homing birds.

562
00:31:43,785 --> 00:31:45,785
I asked if that meant
you would be victorious.

563
00:31:46,705 --> 00:31:47,985
And you smiled and left.

564
00:31:49,025 --> 00:31:50,785
I asked seniors about the meaning,

565
00:31:50,785 --> 00:31:51,866
but they didn't know either.

566
00:31:53,305 --> 00:31:53,945
After that,

567
00:31:53,945 --> 00:31:55,745
I asked many people
before I finally understood.

568
00:31:57,025 --> 00:31:59,066
Since then,

569
00:31:59,666 --> 00:32:02,545
I've known you're a man
standing at the summit.

570
00:32:03,465 --> 00:32:05,106
From the first step out of the gate,

571
00:32:05,785 --> 00:32:08,225
you're a swordsman
who will reach the highest peak.

572
00:32:09,785 --> 00:32:10,386
Bufan.

573
00:32:11,265 --> 00:32:12,106
I believe

574
00:32:12,545 --> 00:32:14,465
your swordsmanship will be famous.

575
00:32:22,386 --> 00:32:22,945
You two.

576
00:32:23,945 --> 00:32:25,225
Could we stop sitting like this now?

577
00:32:25,426 --> 00:32:26,305
It's tiring.

578
00:32:27,626 --> 00:32:29,945
If anyone sees you,

579
00:32:30,025 --> 00:32:32,705
you can explain
you're pursuing pleasure.

580
00:32:32,785 --> 00:32:34,745
My hands are getting tired.

581
00:32:34,745 --> 00:32:35,945
You're a martial artist.

582
00:32:35,945 --> 00:32:37,225
Why are you worn out so soon?

583
00:32:37,666 --> 00:32:38,945
You just mentioned

584
00:32:38,945 --> 00:32:40,785
that Liu Lin came into the Futu Temple

585
00:32:40,785 --> 00:32:42,146
with Men Sandao.

586
00:32:42,146 --> 00:32:42,720
That's right.

587
00:32:43,985 --> 00:32:45,426
It seems that Liu Lin

588
00:32:45,426 --> 00:32:47,386
has useful clues.

589
00:32:47,465 --> 00:32:50,305
Otherwise, Men Sandao
couldn't have taken her with him.

590
00:32:50,866 --> 00:32:53,066
What's Zhuo Bufan's next plan?

591
00:32:53,066 --> 00:32:54,066
To go to Shuntian.

592
00:32:54,066 --> 00:32:55,505
First, report to Prince Qi.

593
00:32:56,386 --> 00:32:58,626
Second, Zhuo Bufan wants to find out

594
00:32:58,626 --> 00:32:59,586
more information,

595
00:33:00,265 --> 00:33:02,186
trying to find

596
00:33:02,186 --> 00:33:03,626
the remaining seal.

597
00:33:03,866 --> 00:33:04,586
Third,

598
00:33:04,745 --> 00:33:07,985
Men Sandao is likely
to return to the capital.

599
00:33:08,505 --> 00:33:10,785
So, Zhuo Bufan also wants

600
00:33:10,985 --> 00:33:13,586
to seize the seal from Men Sandao.

601
00:33:23,025 --> 00:33:23,616
Shall we talk?

602
00:33:24,745 --> 00:33:25,666
I dare not.

603
00:33:25,666 --> 00:33:26,985
I remember your punishment.

604
00:33:27,106 --> 00:33:28,386
It's good.

605
00:33:29,106 --> 00:33:31,106
You are a rebel against the court.

606
00:33:31,106 --> 00:33:32,666
I am an imperial guard,

607
00:33:33,346 --> 00:33:34,545
a hound.

608
00:33:34,985 --> 00:33:35,906
Right.

609
00:33:35,906 --> 00:33:37,186
I'm a rebel

610
00:33:37,186 --> 00:33:38,985
who is falling into your hands.

611
00:33:38,985 --> 00:33:40,866
I will be killed in the end, right?

612
00:33:40,866 --> 00:33:41,626
What's there to fear?

613
00:33:41,626 --> 00:33:42,666
Just be beheaded.

614
00:33:42,666 --> 00:33:44,626
Revolutionaries don't
care about life anyway?

615
00:33:54,705 --> 00:33:55,586
Sir...

616
00:33:56,586 --> 00:33:57,186
Call me Hound.

617
00:33:57,545 --> 00:33:58,186
Hound.

618
00:33:58,666 --> 00:34:00,146
You are not an ordinary hound.

619
00:34:01,066 --> 00:34:02,505
You don't want to treat me this way.

620
00:34:02,545 --> 00:34:03,945
Even if I am not afraid to die,

621
00:34:03,945 --> 00:34:05,305
you still cherish my life.

622
00:34:05,426 --> 00:34:07,265
Are you really not afraid

623
00:34:07,265 --> 00:34:08,305
of death?

624
00:34:08,666 --> 00:34:09,985
Are you gonna say

625
00:34:10,146 --> 00:34:10,906
if I reveal the secret

626
00:34:10,906 --> 00:34:12,705
of the Bodhi Seal,

627
00:34:12,705 --> 00:34:14,186
you will immediately let me go?

628
00:34:14,186 --> 00:34:16,386
You'll personally escort me to the dock,

629
00:34:16,386 --> 00:34:18,945
buy me a ship ticket to Hong Kong, China
or Southeast Asia,

630
00:34:18,945 --> 00:34:20,385
escort me away safely,

631
00:34:21,146 --> 00:34:22,466
and give me some money

632
00:34:22,466 --> 00:34:23,785
as a token of your goodwill.

633
00:34:24,305 --> 00:34:25,265
What a pity.

634
00:34:25,265 --> 00:34:26,825
You're a revolutionary.

635
00:34:26,825 --> 00:34:28,506
Saving your life can't tempt you.

636
00:34:29,026 --> 00:34:29,946
Moreover,

637
00:34:30,265 --> 00:34:31,825
the lives of revolutionaries

638
00:34:31,825 --> 00:34:33,946
cannot be measured by money.

639
00:34:34,425 --> 00:34:35,745
Your original mission

640
00:34:35,745 --> 00:34:37,026
was to protect Tan Xian

641
00:34:37,026 --> 00:34:39,546
and safely hand over the Altar Treasure
to Tongmenghui.

642
00:34:40,225 --> 00:34:41,865
What is this treasure for?

643
00:34:42,106 --> 00:34:43,200
It's for the revolution.

644
00:34:43,200 --> 00:34:44,705
It's to overthrow
the Qing Imperial Court,

645
00:34:44,705 --> 00:34:47,186
that is, the decaying court.

646
00:34:47,586 --> 00:34:49,146
How could you possibly reveal the secret

647
00:34:49,146 --> 00:34:50,666
to me, a hound?

648
00:34:52,186 --> 00:34:53,425
In the Futu Temple,

649
00:34:53,745 --> 00:34:55,705
both you and I know the situation
about the Altar Treasure.

650
00:34:56,506 --> 00:34:58,425
Zhuo Bufan has the Discipline Seal.

651
00:34:58,425 --> 00:35:00,745
Merely with the Bodhi Seal,

652
00:35:00,745 --> 00:35:02,506
I surely can't find the treasure.

653
00:35:02,506 --> 00:35:03,146
Exactly.

654
00:35:03,825 --> 00:35:04,905
The Department

655
00:35:04,905 --> 00:35:06,705
has openly looked for the treasure

656
00:35:06,986 --> 00:35:08,546
for over a century,

657
00:35:08,865 --> 00:35:10,705
but they failed
because the treasure map was incomplete.

658
00:35:11,385 --> 00:35:12,506
Even if Tongmenghui

659
00:35:12,506 --> 00:35:14,066
has half of the treasure map,

660
00:35:14,066 --> 00:35:15,466
we can only search furtively.

661
00:35:15,705 --> 00:35:17,586
I'm afraid
it will take hundreds of years.

662
00:35:17,586 --> 00:35:18,865
Then the revolution is hopeless.

663
00:35:18,865 --> 00:35:19,705
Exactly.

664
00:35:20,146 --> 00:35:21,666
This treasure map means nothing

665
00:35:21,666 --> 00:35:23,546
to me and Tongmenghui.

666
00:35:24,106 --> 00:35:25,986
I might as well trade it
for my life or freedom.

667
00:35:25,986 --> 00:35:27,425
This is all for my own good.

668
00:35:27,425 --> 00:35:30,225
If I lose my life for
such an insignificant thing,

669
00:35:30,225 --> 00:35:33,265
I'll be helpless to the revolution.

670
00:35:33,905 --> 00:35:35,345
It's no use talking about these.

671
00:35:35,946 --> 00:35:37,986
Even if I threaten to kill you,
you still won't tell me.

672
00:35:37,986 --> 00:35:39,546
You must think now

673
00:35:39,546 --> 00:35:41,425
that my master Cheng Yu,
the chief inheritor

674
00:35:41,425 --> 00:35:42,825
of the Southern Shaolin,

675
00:35:42,825 --> 00:35:44,586
is such a fool.

676
00:35:44,586 --> 00:35:45,546
He chose me,

677
00:35:45,546 --> 00:35:47,345
a hound,

678
00:35:47,345 --> 00:35:48,586
as his inheritor.

679
00:35:48,586 --> 00:35:50,146
Don't belittle yourself.

680
00:35:50,506 --> 00:35:52,626
Since I'm so obstinate

681
00:35:52,626 --> 00:35:53,705
and unenlightened,

682
00:35:53,705 --> 00:35:55,506
you might have to keep me by your side.

683
00:35:55,506 --> 00:35:56,946
Anyway, you don't think I'm a burden.

684
00:35:56,946 --> 00:35:58,785
If you don't care, why should I?

685
00:35:58,785 --> 00:36:00,066
It's for my own good.

686
00:36:00,666 --> 00:36:02,146
I'm a rebel.

687
00:36:02,146 --> 00:36:03,385
If others catch me,

688
00:36:03,385 --> 00:36:04,865
I'll be interrogated and punished.

689
00:36:04,865 --> 00:36:06,186
I'll suffer torment.

690
00:36:06,186 --> 00:36:07,146
It doesn't work.

691
00:36:07,146 --> 00:36:08,946
You're not even afraid of death.

692
00:36:09,666 --> 00:36:11,506
So you've never told anyone

693
00:36:12,345 --> 00:36:14,506
that I'm the one
who holds the secret of the Bodhi Seal.

694
00:36:15,106 --> 00:36:16,265
Even your subordinates

695
00:36:16,905 --> 00:36:18,865
and Beiyang Army
you're working with didn't know it.

696
00:36:19,626 --> 00:36:20,345
I haven't told them,

697
00:36:20,345 --> 00:36:22,026
because I want to keep this secret.

698
00:36:22,425 --> 00:36:23,785
If others find it out,

699
00:36:23,785 --> 00:36:25,825
more people will keep an eye on you.

700
00:36:26,066 --> 00:36:28,345
If so, I'll be distracted.

701
00:36:29,186 --> 00:36:30,066
So no worries.

702
00:36:30,865 --> 00:36:32,305
I won't tell anyone you're the inheritor

703
00:36:32,305 --> 00:36:33,146
of the Bodhi Department.

704
00:36:33,666 --> 00:36:34,865
I'll not cause you any trouble.

705
00:36:38,026 --> 00:36:39,506
Talking with a clever person like you

706
00:36:39,506 --> 00:36:40,626
is quite troublesome.

707
00:36:40,626 --> 00:36:42,626
You've said everything I wanted to say.

708
00:36:42,865 --> 00:36:44,745
Haven't you said what I wanted to say?

709
00:36:51,146 --> 00:36:52,305
You really can't tell me?

710
00:36:56,705 --> 00:36:57,865
I'm truly not afraid of death.

711
00:37:12,305 --> 00:37:13,385
Don't move.

712
00:37:14,466 --> 00:37:15,066
Miss Lin.

713
00:37:15,626 --> 00:37:16,905
I can do it myself.

714
00:37:17,026 --> 00:37:17,568
I...

715
00:37:19,225 --> 00:37:20,986
I can't help you with the big matters,

716
00:37:21,586 --> 00:37:23,546
but I can help you with small things.

717
00:37:25,186 --> 00:37:25,792
Be good.

718
00:37:26,186 --> 00:37:26,912
Don't move.

719
00:37:29,026 --> 00:37:29,626
Okay.

720
00:37:29,626 --> 00:37:30,666
I-I won't move.

721
00:37:33,626 --> 00:37:34,506
Go on.

722
00:37:34,905 --> 00:37:35,546
Say what?

723
00:37:38,385 --> 00:37:39,186
You don't trust him?

724
00:37:43,865 --> 00:37:45,425
Muqing is a gentleman.

725
00:37:45,425 --> 00:37:46,905
If he hides the information

726
00:37:47,666 --> 00:37:48,865
of secret treasure from me,

727
00:37:48,865 --> 00:37:49,705
I can understand.

728
00:37:51,305 --> 00:37:52,586
Aren't you two cooperating?

729
00:37:52,825 --> 00:37:54,546
It doesn't mean sharing everything.

730
00:37:55,506 --> 00:37:58,466
If he wants to capture Zhuo Bufan,

731
00:37:59,066 --> 00:38:01,146
isn't it a good thing for you?

732
00:38:02,666 --> 00:38:04,066
His goal is to find the treasure.

733
00:38:04,066 --> 00:38:05,946
If Zhuo Bufan is caught by him,

734
00:38:05,946 --> 00:38:07,506
in exchange for the seal,

735
00:38:08,305 --> 00:38:09,865
Muqing will certainly agree

736
00:38:09,865 --> 00:38:10,745
to release Zhuo Bufan.

737
00:38:12,345 --> 00:38:13,186
Will he?

738
00:38:13,186 --> 00:38:13,905
Yes, he will.

739
00:38:15,026 --> 00:38:16,946
Muqing does appreciate me,

740
00:38:17,785 --> 00:38:18,865
but that's all.

741
00:38:19,425 --> 00:38:21,146
In major issues,

742
00:38:21,146 --> 00:38:21,905
he has no choice.

743
00:38:22,666 --> 00:38:23,425
You are right.

744
00:38:24,865 --> 00:38:27,425
If Zhuo Bufan collaborates
with the Imperial Household Department,

745
00:38:28,146 --> 00:38:30,905
he could use them to eliminate you.

746
00:38:32,466 --> 00:38:34,265
So I must find Zhuo Bufan first

747
00:38:34,986 --> 00:38:35,986
to take the advantage.

748
00:38:37,506 --> 00:38:38,106
Fortunately,

749
00:38:38,785 --> 00:38:39,785
you have Beiyang Army's guns.

750
00:38:41,265 --> 00:38:42,825
Beiyang Army is
looking for the treasure too.

751
00:38:43,385 --> 00:38:45,066
After finding the treasure,
Beiyang Army can work

752
00:38:46,026 --> 00:38:47,705
with the Imperial Household Department.

753
00:38:48,265 --> 00:38:50,186
After all, they all serve the court.

754
00:38:53,026 --> 00:38:55,466
I have let Ding Yu send people
to investigate it,

755
00:38:56,026 --> 00:38:58,425
but there are no traces
of people from the Rongtian Ridge.

756
00:38:58,946 --> 00:39:00,626
I don't know where they will go.

757
00:39:02,745 --> 00:39:04,066
Doesn't the Department look for them?

758
00:39:06,146 --> 00:39:07,986
I guess Muqing
deliberately doesn't look for them.

759
00:39:09,546 --> 00:39:10,905
As Muqing said,

760
00:39:10,905 --> 00:39:12,146
there are two seals.

761
00:39:12,146 --> 00:39:13,705
Zhuo Bufan certainly needs the one

762
00:39:13,705 --> 00:39:14,946
in Muqing's hands.

763
00:39:15,506 --> 00:39:17,546
Didn't he find nothing at Futu Temple?

764
00:39:19,265 --> 00:39:20,466
Even I don't believe it,

765
00:39:21,425 --> 00:39:22,865
let alone Zhuo Bufan.

766
00:39:23,265 --> 00:39:24,506
And Muqing knows

767
00:39:24,506 --> 00:39:25,986
Zhuo Bufan won't believe it.

768
00:39:27,026 --> 00:39:27,785
Therefore,

769
00:39:28,705 --> 00:39:30,745
Muqing is waiting for Zhuo Bufan
to come to him.

770
00:39:31,666 --> 00:39:33,146
But Zhuo Bufan doesn't go to him.

771
00:39:34,225 --> 00:39:34,986
I don't think

772
00:39:34,986 --> 00:39:36,626
Zhuo Bufan is afraid of Muqing

773
00:39:36,626 --> 00:39:38,546
or the masters in the imperial yamen.

774
00:39:38,546 --> 00:39:40,106
Will he be wary of you?

775
00:39:40,106 --> 00:39:41,186
You have a gun, after all.

776
00:39:41,825 --> 00:39:43,345
At first, I thought so too.

777
00:39:43,345 --> 00:39:44,705
But later I don't think so.

778
00:39:45,546 --> 00:39:47,785
Although Zhuo Bufan is wary of our guns,

779
00:39:48,026 --> 00:39:48,825
he's not afraid.

780
00:39:49,546 --> 00:39:51,225
Treasure matters to him.

781
00:39:51,225 --> 00:39:52,026
He can't be afraid.

782
00:39:53,106 --> 00:39:53,946
So...

783
00:39:53,946 --> 00:39:54,745
So,

784
00:39:55,506 --> 00:39:57,385
Zhuo Bufan should have more clues.

785
00:39:58,745 --> 00:40:00,626
Though he gets nothing from Futu Temple,

786
00:40:01,425 --> 00:40:02,586
he won't give up.

787
00:40:02,865 --> 00:40:04,066
Since what happened in Shanghai,

788
00:40:04,705 --> 00:40:06,345
the Rongtian Ridge has been acting

789
00:40:06,345 --> 00:40:07,705
ahead of the Department.

790
00:40:07,905 --> 00:40:10,905
Is Zhuo Bufan waiting for Muqing
to come to him?

791
00:40:11,026 --> 00:40:12,385
Zhuo Bufan is proud.

792
00:40:13,066 --> 00:40:14,186
He will not think that way.

793
00:40:14,865 --> 00:40:15,466
Moreover,

794
00:40:17,865 --> 00:40:19,506
I don't
want the Imperial Household Department

795
00:40:19,506 --> 00:40:20,506
to meet with Rongtian Ridge.

796
00:40:20,986 --> 00:40:22,705
After all, they might cooperate.

797
00:40:23,305 --> 00:40:25,146
It's such a large treasure.

798
00:40:25,666 --> 00:40:27,466
If the Rongtian Ridge gets a bit of it,

799
00:40:28,425 --> 00:40:30,026
I'm afraid it will suffice for them.

800
00:40:32,385 --> 00:40:33,546
I think

801
00:40:34,026 --> 00:40:35,905
I should find Zhuo Bufan
and the others first.

802
00:40:36,825 --> 00:40:37,345
That's good.

803
00:40:38,026 --> 00:40:39,385
In the beginning,

804
00:40:39,586 --> 00:40:40,745
my target is Zhuo Bufan

805
00:40:41,066 --> 00:40:42,186
and the Rongtian Ridge.

806
00:40:59,425 --> 00:41:00,066
Besides,

807
00:41:02,946 --> 00:41:03,825
I've promised you

808
00:41:05,225 --> 00:41:07,265
I'll bring the murderers to justice.

809
00:41:11,946 --> 00:41:13,506
I've always believed in you.

810
00:41:33,506 --> 00:41:34,385
According to Zhuangzi,

811
00:41:34,825 --> 00:41:36,345
