00:41:51,345 --> 00:41:52,466
So were you used

822
00:41:52,466 --> 00:41:53,546
or I burned bridges?

823
00:41:54,586 --> 00:41:56,106
It doesn't matter.

824
00:41:56,106 --> 00:41:57,066
What's important is you.

825
00:41:57,385 --> 00:41:58,905
You're so ungrateful.

826
00:42:00,586 --> 00:42:02,825
Without me,
could you think of the Futu Temple?

827
00:42:03,146 --> 00:42:05,586
